---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6 text-gray-800 dark:text-white">About Us</h1>
    
    <div class="prose dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
      <p>
        Welcome to the Rule One Assistant, your companion tool for applying Phil Town's Rule #1 investing principles. 
        Our mission is to empower individual investors with the tools and insights needed to make confident, informed decisions 
        and achieve long-term financial success by investing in wonderful companies at attractive prices.
      </p>
      
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Our Philosophy</h2>
      <p>
        We believe that successful investing doesn't have to be complicated. By following the time-tested strategies outlined by 
        Phil Town, anyone can learn to identify great businesses and determine when they represent a compelling investment opportunity. 
        This application is designed to streamline that process, from initial stock screening to detailed valuation.
      </p>
      
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">What We Offer</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Stock Screening:</strong> Find companies that meet the qualitative and quantitative criteria of a "wonderful business."</li>
        <li><strong>Valuation Tools:</strong> Calculate sticker price and margin of safety using established Rule #1 methods.</li>
        <li><strong>Watchlist Management:</strong> Keep track of companies you're monitoring.</li>
        <li><strong>Educational Resources:</strong> (Coming Soon) Links and summaries to help you deepen your understanding of Rule #1 investing.</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Our Team</h2>
      <p>
        We are a passionate group of developers and investors dedicated to making sophisticated investing strategies accessible to everyone. 
        We are continuously working to improve the Rule One Assistant and add new features to support your investment journey.
      </p>
      
      <p class="mt-8">
        Thank you for using the Rule One Assistant. We're excited to be a part of your path to financial freedom!
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
